OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FComedian Vir Das causes a  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstir with 'two Indias'     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fmonologue                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A monologue by one of India's top      
OL,6, comedians has outraged some in the     
OL,7, country, prompting complaints to police
OL,8, and criticism from fellow performers.  
OL,10,FDuring his show in the US, Vir Das     
OL,11,Fdescribed a country of two sides where 
OL,12,Fpeople "worship women during the day   
OL,13,Fbut gang rape them at night".          
OL,15,FIn response to the strong backlash, he 
OL,16,Fcalled it "satire about the duality of 
OL,17,Ftwo very separate Indias".             
OL,19,FOthers have shown support for the      
OL,20,Fcomic, who received a standing ovation.
